            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_018P7fBkdJeKaFYh7M9sScom\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01QDFUG38VRZX3rCjbs2W8rP\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"I appreciate that you're passionate about pasta — that's actually a great starting point! But I'm noticing we've shifted away from your business idea (Friend of the Pod, the podcast matchmaking service).\\n\\nHere's the gap: \\\"I like pasta\\\" is a personal preference, but what we need is the *business idea*. So let me ask directly:\\n\\n**What do you actually DO with pasta? Or is this a separate business idea altogether?**\\n\\nAre you thinking about:\\n- A pasta-themed podcast or podcast network?\\n- A service that connects pasta brands with food podcasters?\\n- Something else entirely?\\n\\nI want to make sure we're building on the momentum from Friend of the Pod, or if you've pivoted to something new. Either way is fine — I just need to know what we're actually working with so we can make it remarkable.\",\"examples\":[\"I'm launching a podcast about pasta-making techniques and want to connect with culinary experts as guests\",\"I'm building a marketplace where pasta brands can sponsor food and lifestyle podcasts\",\"I'm creating a pasta delivery service and want to use podcasting as my marketing channel\"],\"conclusion\":\"You've got good instincts — you just need to translate that passion into a specific business model. Once you do, we'll have something real to work with.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1795,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":336,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
