        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1604,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1604,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01KB4UArQmQ6ycvRhkjrMvX5\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01Km2x3CTgoVJiYYDXpfvbbK\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"You've built something genuinely useful—AI matching that saves hosts hours finding quality guests. Now the question: who's already benefiting, and can you show it?\\n\\nSince you're early-stage (no testimonials yet), we're looking at founder credibility, beta results, or early wins. Here's what I need:\\n\\n**Have you:**\\n- Tested with real podcast hosts? How many? What happened?\\n- Seen measurable results (time saved, guest quality, listener feedback)?\\n- Built this from personal pain (your own podcast struggles)?\\n- Got beta users or early adopters willing to vouch?\\n\\nPick the strongest one—that's your proof.\",\"examples\":[\"Founder story: \\\"I spent 40 hrs/month finding guests for my show. Built this to solve it. Now hosts do it in 15 mins.\\\"\",\"Beta proof: \\\"50 hosts tested it. Average time to find guest: 8 mins vs. 2 hours before.\\\"\",\"Personal transformation: \\\"Went from 2 guests/month to 8. Show quality jumped. Here's the data.\\\"\"],\"conclusion\":\"You don't need 100 testimonials yet. One strong proof point—real numbers, real person, real result—beats generic praise every time. What's your strongest story?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2297,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":341,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
