            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01265LJGvwRYRxQKh7xQLmLk\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_013abtWGNoq3PyQes8Fo8Dgz\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"I see you love pasta—that's genuine! But we need to bridge from personal passion to actual business idea.\\n\\nThe gap: \\\"I like pasta\\\" is a preference, not a business model. We need to know: **What do you actually DO with pasta? Who would pay for it? What problem does it solve?**\\n\\nAre you thinking:\\n- Selling pasta products (fresh, specialty, imported)?\\n- Teaching people to make pasta (classes, content)?\\n- Connecting pasta lovers with restaurants or recipes?\\n- Something else entirely?\\n\\nPick one direction and tell us: Who's frustrated, and how does your pasta idea fix it?\",\"examples\":[\"I'm selling handmade fresh pasta to busy professionals who want quality but don't have time to make it\",\"I'm teaching home cooks authentic Italian pasta techniques because most YouTube tutorials skip the fundamentals\",\"I'm building a community app for pasta enthusiasts to share recipes and find local pasta makers\"],\"conclusion\":\"Your passion is the starting point—now let's turn it into something people will actually seek out and pay for.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1815,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":286,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
