            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01CsTTRywSy6ZHBhftV6ZxzQ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01E4g3fy4e7yDmVHeNfUFxZ5\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"I love the matchmaking angle—that's a real mechanism, not just \\\"helping people.\\\" But \\\"matchmaking service\\\" could mean a dozen different things. \\n\\nWho are you actually connecting? Are you matching:\\n- Podcasters with guest experts?\\n- Listeners with shows they'd love?\\n- Sponsors with creators?\\n- Something else entirely?\\n\\nOnce we nail WHO you're connecting and WHAT problem that solves for them, the whole idea clicks into focus.\",\"examples\":[\"We match indie podcasters with relevant guests so they don't spend 20 hours cold-emailing\",\"We match listeners to niche podcasts they didn't know existed based on their interests\",\"We match sponsors with podcasts in their category to find authentic ad placements\"],\"conclusion\":\"You've got a solid core concept—just need to zoom in on the specific connection you're making and who benefits most.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1645,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":247,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
