            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1244,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01QHUKTamNQsm7RtEwvrzmBV\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01TPyQWbx9T5PsGyDDfJoMWw\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"You've nailed the brainstorming! Now let's talk look and feel for your landing page. Since Friend of the Pod is all about solving the \\\"needle in a haystack\\\" problem for podcast hosts, how do you want your page to *feel*? Should it be sleek and professional? Bold and energetic? Trustworthy and data-driven?\",\"examples\":[\"Sleek + minimal: Clean design, lots of white space, focus on the AI matching magic (feels premium, modern)\",\"Bold + energetic: Vibrant colors, dynamic layout, emphasize the speed/efficiency win (feels like action, momentum)\",\"Data-driven + authoritative: Charts, stats, case studies front-and-center, professional tone (feels credible, proven)\"],\"conclusion\":\"What vibe matches your brand? Or want to skip personalization and just build it now?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3901,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":245,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
